<HEADLINE> "People's Daily" Greeting Opening of Party Congress (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The basic principle of "seizing opportunities, stepping up
reforms, expand the opening-up, furthering development, and
maintaining stability" has been implemented.
</P>
<P>
Work on a socialist market economy framework has speeded up and
the national economy has developed in a sustainable, rapid and
healthy way, moreover, the social productive force, overall
national strength and the people's living standards all have
scaled to a new height.
</P>
<P>
Progress has been made in Party building, providing a clean and
honest government, democratic and legal construction, and in
socialist ethical and cultural progress.
</P>
<P>
Progress has also been made in culture, science and technology,
and education undertakings.
</P>
<P>
National defense has also reported new advances with the still
more consolidated national defense. And thanks to outstanding
achievements scored in diplomatic work, China's international
status has improved with each passing day.
</P>
<P>
With the return of Hong Kong to the motherland, a historical
step has been taken toward reunification of the motherland.
</P>
<P>
So the great motherland is seething with enthusiasm everywhere,
since it has achieved economic growth, political stability,
ethnical unity and social progress.
</P>
<P>
The past five years have been a period of unity for advancement
and glorious achievements. It was the period in which Deng's
theory shone with dazzling splendor and the Party and nation are
proud of these years.
</P>
<P>
History has proven that every major decision made at the 14th
CPC Congress was correct and that the Party Central Committee
leadership with Jiang Zemin at its core has been effective.
</P>
<P>
History has further proven that the road opened up by the
Communist Party to build socialism with Chinese characteristics is
the only broad road to follow in rejuvenating the nation,
developing a strong and prosperous China, and bringing happiness
to the people.
</P>
</TEXT>
