<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, September 11 (Xinhua) -- The Office of the
Commissioner of the Chinese Foreign Ministry in the Hong Kong
Special Administrative Region (SAR) hosted a reception for
Chinese and foreign resident correspondents here this evening.
</P>
<P>
The event was designed to give the press a chance of getting to
know each other and exchange, said Wu Hongbo, chief of the
Information Department of the office.
</P>
<P>
