program instituted by the Camerounian government was already a
step in the fight against economic huddles and poverty.
</P>
<P>
He urged lecturers on economy in Camerounian universities to
help solve the nation's economic problems.
</P>
<P>
For two days, participants at the seminar examined the
degradation of the environment and poverty, identified expenses
on education in developing sub-Sahara Africa. 
