<HEADLINE> "People's Daily" Greeting Opening of Party Congress (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 11 (Xinhua) -- "People's Daily" tomorrow
carries an editorial entitled "Inherit the past and usher in the
future, carry the cause forward and forge ahead into the future"
on the opening session of the 15th National Congress of the
Communist Party of China (CPC).
</P>
<P>
It says that the congress is being held at an important period
of China's reform and opening-up and during the socialist
modernization and has great historical significance.
</P>
<P>
It will ensure that the Party will adhere to its basic theory
and will advance resolutely along the road it has been following
since the Third Plenary Session of the 11th National Congress of
the CPC.
</P>
<P>
The congress will hold high the banner of Deng Xiaoping's
theory of building socialism with Chinese characteristics, review
the Chinese people's history of struggles over the past century,
and look forward to China's development prospects in the first
half of the next century.
</P>
<P>
The congress will also conscientiously summarize its practical
experience since the Third Plenary Session of the 11th CPC
Central Committee, and especially since the 14th CPC National
Congress, and will work out all-round arrangements and
cross-century developments for China's reform and opening-up and
socialist modernization construction.
</P>
<P>
New central leading bodies will be elected and the congress
will arouse the Party and the nation to further emancipate their
thinking, seek truth from facts, seize opportunities, explore and
forge ahead to advance in a comprehensive way socialism with
Chinese characteristics into the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
The 15th Party Congress is convened at a time when new progress
and victories have been scored in the great cause of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics. Since the 14th CPC
National Congress, the whole Party and the people of all ethnic
groups across China, under the leadship of the CPC Central
Committee with Jiang Zemin at its core, have adhered to Deng's
theory and the Party's basic line for the primary stage of
socialism, and made tremendous achievements in all fields.
</P>
</TEXT>
