<TEXT>
<P>
UNITED NATIONS, September 11 (Xinhua) -- U.N. Secretary-General
Kofi Annan today urged the United States to fulfill its
commitments and pay fully its dues to the United Nations.
</P>
<P>
Speaking to reporters, Annan said there had been some progress
in the discussions with Washington regarding the amounts of U.S.
dues to the United Nations, and the bill before the U.S. congress
now was to release the dues to the United Nations.
</P>
