implementing and managing the official development assistance
projects.
</P>
<P>
He also encouraged Nepal's efforts in such sectors as primary
health care, education and environmental protection.
</P>
<P>
Nepali Finance Secretary Ram Binod Bhattarai, who led the
Nepali side at the meeting, said Japan's cooperation is expected
for the successful implementation of Nepal's ninth five-year plan
(1997-2002).
</P>
<P>
Japan is a member country of the Nepal Aid Group.  
