Jiang's report will enhance the consent of understanding by our
Taiwan compatriots, who are welcomed to make positive proposals on
realizing the peaceful reunificaition," she said.
</P>
<P>
Another delegate, Ni Runfeng, chairman of the board of
directors of Changhong Group, a successful state-owned firm in
Sichuan, said the 15th Party congress is geared to the development
in the 21st century. It will work out the theory, principles and
programs for China's development in the next century.
</P>
