Insurance giant FAI rose one cent to 61 cents after it posted a
57 percent increase in annual net profit.
</P>
<P>
The gold index closed 3.3 points down at 1,288.1.
</P>
<P>
National turnover totaled 368.43 million Shares traded with
value of 845.39 million Australian dollars (608.68 million U.S.
dollars), falling stocks outnumbered rising stocks by 627 to 408.
 
