over 85.68 million yuan (10.3 million US dollars) and exported
goods valued at 16.83 million US dollars during the first seven
months of this year.
</P>
<P>
The official promised greater support for the 10 enterprises in
terms of export and import quotas, and customs inspections.
</P>
<P>
