transition of China's economic mechanisms during their visit to a
number of Chinese cities and learned more about how small cities
like like Zhuhai have evolved into large modern cities, the
president noted.
</P>
<P>
Constantinescu briefed Zhuhai government officials and
entrepreneurs on his country's foreign policy and social and
economic situation.
</P>
