<HEADLINE> 15th CPC National Congress Opens (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Then, all present observed a silence in memory of the
late proletarian revolutionaries including Mao Zedong, Zhou Enlai,
Liu Shaoqi, Zhu De, Deng Xiaoping, Chen Yun and Peng Zhen.
</P>
<P>
Li Peng announced that current congress has 2,048 delegates and
60 specially invited delegates, 2,074 of whom attended today's
opening session.
