<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Jiang Zemin Delivers Report at 15th Party Congress (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 12 (Xinhua) -- Jiang Zemin, general
secretary of the Communist Party of China (CPC), delivered a
report on behalf of the 14th CPC Central Committee at the CPC 15th
National Congress which was opened here today.
</P>
<P>
The report is entitled "Hold High the Great Banner of Deng
Xiaoping Theory for an All-Round Advancement of the Cause of
Building Socialism With Chinese Characteristics to the 21st
Century". It has 10 parts: 1. Looking Back and Ahead at the Turn
of the Century; 2. Work of the Past Five Years; 3. Historical
Status and Guiding Significance of Deng Xiaoping Theory; 4. The
Basic Line and Program for the Primary Stage of Socialism; 5.
Economic Restructuring and Economic Development Strategy; 6.
Reforming the Political Structure and Strengthening Democracy and
the Legal System; 7. Developing Socialist Culture With Chinese
Characteristics; 8. Promoting the Peaceful Reunification of the
Motherland; 9. The International Situation and Our Foreign Policy;
and 10. the Communist Party of China Facing the New Century.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said that the theme of the congress is to hold high the
great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory for an all-round advancement
of the cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics to
the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
He stressed that the issue of the banner is of the utmost
importance. The banner represents China's orientation and image.
Firmly adhering to the party's line means firmly upholding the
banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory.
</P>
<P>
The CPC Central Committee proposes, Jiang said, that the Party,
at its 15th Congress, establish Deng Xiaoping Theory as its
guiding ideology by stipulating in its Constitution that the
Chinese Communist Party takes Marxism-Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought
and Deng Xiaoping Theory as its guide to action.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said Deng Xiaoping Theory is Marxism of present-day
China, representing a new stage of development of Marxism in
China.
</P>
<P>
In China today, it is Deng Xiaoping Theory, which integrates
Marxism with the practice of present-day China and the features of
the times, and this theory alone, that can settle the issues
concerning the future and destiny of socialism. The soul of the
current congress, he said, is to hold high the great banner of
Deng Xiaoping Theory, which will be the hallmark of this congress
in the annals of history.
</P>
</TEXT>
